The Zondo Commission of Inquiry is hearing Bosasa related testimony. JOHANNESBURG - ANC MP Vincent Smith is on the stand at the Zondo Commission of Inquiry. The commission is hearing Bosasa related testimony. Smith and several senior ANC members have been implicated in former Bosasa COO Angelo Agrizzi's testimony. WATCH: WATCH: Mokonyane backtracks on ‘surprise’ birthday bash Agrizzi has told the commission Smith was paid hundreds of thousands of rand. Smith confirmed some payments but says they were personal loans. The now-defunct Bosasa netted billions from government contracts for years.